  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR's Ultimate Obstacle Course & Test of Fitness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obsessed with his family's legacy, aging billionaire Adam Venture is looking for a capable heir to the Venture name and fortune. His only requirement? The skill and tenacity to overcome a series of deadly obstacle courses known as: Venture’s Gauntlet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/6b28e43453b56fe58e900295b962de9e.poster.avif?t=1760965647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/6b28e43453b56fe58e900295b962de9e.webm?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/6b28e43453b56fe58e900295b962de9e.mp4?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Comfortable Locomotion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, climb, swing and zipline your way through the gauntlet in comfort and style with TrueMotionVR arm swing controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome Dangerous Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killer-drones, deadly lasers, fatal drops and more all stand along the path to glory. Only the most capable will survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/717e1871af2dfba8478ace6c85b7630b.poster.avif?t=1760965647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/717e1871af2dfba8478ace6c85b7630b.webm?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/717e1871af2dfba8478ace6c85b7630b.mp4?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Embark On An Epic Journey</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse giant cliffs, delve into the depths of the earth and climb crumbling castles across 9 intense stages inspired by the Highlands of Scotland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/3b3b22978e3ee886a545f71636058bcd.poster.avif?t=1760965647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/3b3b22978e3ee886a545f71636058bcd.webm?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/3b3b22978e3ee886a545f71636058bcd.mp4?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breathtaking Visuals - Experience beautiful graphics powered by Unreal Engine. A dynamic time of day and weather system makes the world feel alive as you progress through the Gauntlet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the secrets of the Ventures - The ever-present Adam Venture watches your every move. Do you have the skill to impress him or will you be a disappointment like all the others?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tailor Made Courses - Calibration adjusts the Gauntlet’s obstacles to your height & arm length measurements to ensure the best experience for all users.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claim the ultimate glory - Compete against other players for the best times on each stage on the online leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level Up Your Fitness - Venture’s Gauntlet is the most difficult parkour/assault course experience currently available on VR–you will be physically challenged when playing this game!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR's Ultimate Obstacle Course & Test of Fitness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obsessed with his family's legacy, aging billionaire Adam Venture is looking for a capable heir to the Venture name and fortune. His only requirement? The skill and tenacity to overcome a series of deadly obstacle courses known as: Venture’s Gauntlet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/6b28e43453b56fe58e900295b962de9e.poster.avif?t=1760965647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/6b28e43453b56fe58e900295b962de9e.webm?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/6b28e43453b56fe58e900295b962de9e.mp4?t=1760965647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Comfortable Locomotion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, climb, swing and zipline your way through the gauntlet in comfort and style with TrueMotionVR arm swing controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome Dangerous Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killer-drones, deadly lasers, fatal drops and more all stand along the path to glory. Only the most capable will survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras/717e1871af2dfba8478ace6c85b7630b.poster.avif?t=1760965647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840140/extras